Text: Re Hibuddywhat is up WI am just getting ready to leave work and head home to Denver tomorrow morning for the week My oldest bro had a baby last week and my other bro got engaged and there is a huge party for them tomorrow i am super excited because it fall on the long weekend I will be skiing in Steambost this weekend However Tahoe has been getting dumped on I am too broke to even go skiing out herethe gas bill is Killing me tee hee Actually we do not even turn on our heat because our place is very hard to keep warmthe hard wood floors and the tall ceilings As for SF everything is great i love it but I need to get a better paying job because I am broke Oh well I need to do it while I am young and fins some rich guy just kidding Anyway How are you doing Any ladies strikin your fancy this valentines day Previous Message from on PM To Anne echtvcorp cc Subject Re Hi did you go and sign up on that website there are a lot of people from our class on there what is going on how is san francisco can you pay your gas bill i trade energy in that area how is the nightlife are you dating at all life here is hectic i have just been working and going out when are you going home again i dont know when i will get back there but i wish i was going back to ski shoot me an email when you get a chance
